    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> and <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 5 min, then reduce the heat to low and cook for a further 15 min or until softened and caramelised</p>",
