    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Bash the <strong>lemongrass stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>with a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, cut down the middle lengthways, remove the <strong>tough</strong> <strong>outer layers</strong> and set aside for later, then chop the <strong>soft inner core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p>",
