      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basmati rice </strong>with 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>cold water </strong>and the<strong> outer lemongrass</strong> <strong>layers </strong>to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p>",
