    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped lemongrass core</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong> and<strong> nigella seeds</strong> to the onion pan and cook for 2 min</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
