    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>golden</strong> <strong>paneer</strong> to the pan with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong></p><p>Mix well and cook for a further 5 min or until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Once thickened, stir through the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>paneer, pepper & lemongrass curry</strong></p>",
